### computeCUSignature() {#ad27bf36fbf19cdf6d2e5a9dfeebaf260}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>uint64&#95;t DIEHash::computeCUSignature (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringref">StringRef</a> DWOName, <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> &amp; Die)</>}>
Computes the <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/cu">CU</a> signature.

This is based on the type signature computation given in section 7.27 of the DWARF4 standard.

It is an md5 hash of the flattened description of the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> with the inclusion of the full <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/cu">CU</a> and all top level <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/cu">CU</a> entities.

Declaration at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/asmprinter/diehash-h/#l00038">38</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/asmprinter/diehash-h">DIEHash.h</a>, definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/asmprinter/diehash-cpp/#l00399">399</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/asmprinter/diehash-cpp">DIEHash.cpp</a>.
</MemberDefinition>

### computeTypeSignature() {#a22e2fce16609b6482e290f3f24172f85}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>uint64&#95;t DIEHash::computeTypeSignature (<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> &amp; Die)</>}>
Computes the type signature.

This is based on the type signature computation given in section 7.27 of the DWARF4 standard.

It is an md5 hash of the flattened description of the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> with the inclusion of additional forms not specifically called out in the standard.
